To create a zip archive of a file, run:
zip code.zip file

To create a zip archive of a directory, run:
zip -r code.zip java

To exclude a directory, run:
zip -r code.zip java -x \*docs/*

To exclude hidden files, run:
zip -r code.zip java -x \*/.*
to archive a folder run zip -r name.zip folder/

to archive a folder and exclude files, run
zip -r code.zip ./ -x '.*'
